Package lib.homies.framework

Class HomiesLib

java.lang.Object
lib.homies.framework.HomiesLib
public final class HomiesLib extends Object
The central service locator for the HomiesLib framework. Provides static access to all registered platform-agnostic services. This class is initialized by the platform-specific plugin (e.g., HomiesLibSpigot) on server startup.
